                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9896" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0124</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1165 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从寒流到暖意：哈尔滨冰雪大世界的退票风波与品牌重塑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Cold Wave to Warmth: The Refund Incident and Brand Reinvention of Harbin Ice and Snow World</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邵景波，吴少辉，李鹏宇，王舒祺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨冰雪大世界股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">危机管理；品牌重塑；市场营销；2025百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Crisis management, Brand reconstruction, Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦哈尔滨冰雪大世界的退票危机与品牌重塑过程。2023年12月18日，第二十五届冰雪大世界开园首日因游客量远超园区最大承载量（实际4.5万人/预计1万人），导致排队系统崩溃、服务设施瘫痪，负面舆情迅速发酵。董事长郭宏伟迅速决策，关闭售票系统、设立临时退票中心，并通过员工电子支付垫付机制完成约7000张退票，同时提供御寒物资与实时信息更新，逐步控制事态。危机后，园区通过硬件升级、服务优化及舆情闭环管理，成功实现品牌形象修复。本案例适用于《危机管理》《市场营销》等课程，通过危机阶段模型、情境危机沟通理论等框架，分析危机预警、决策逻辑与舆情应对策略。启发思考题涵盖危机阶段划分、消费者心理、地域认同影响及品牌建设思维，旨在培养学员的系统性危机处理能力与长效管理思维。案例附详细教学说明、理论依据及课堂计划，助力学员从实践角度掌握“危机转化”的核心逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case examines the refund crisis and brand reinvention of Harbin Ice and Snow World. On December 18, 2023, the opening day of the 25th Ice and Snow World, the park’s operations collapsed due to a surge in tourist numbers (Actual: 45,000/ Expected: 10,000), leading to system failures and widespread negative publicity. Chairman Guo Hongwei swiftly implemented emergency measures, including suspending ticket sales, establishing a refund center, and initiating an employee e-payment advance mechanism to process approximately 7,000 refunds. While also providing cold-weather supplies and real-time information updates to gradually bring the situation under control. Post-crisis, the park upgraded facilities, optimized services, and established a closed-loop public opinion management system. Designed for courses like Crisis Management and Marketing, this case leverages frameworks such as the Crisis Stage Model and Situational Crisis Communication Theory (SCCT) to analyze crisis prevention, decision-making, and reputation recovery. Discussion questions explore crisis phases, consumer psychology, regional identity dynamics, and sustainable brand strategies. Supported by teaching notes, theoretical foundations, and classroom plans, the case equips learners with practical insights into transforming crises into opportunities for systemic improvement.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《危机管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">危机阶段模型，情境危机沟通理论，新媒体营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
